overview:
This German IP Lawyer firm offers legal advice in the field of intellectual property law.

Protection rights such patent, trademark, design in Europe and Germany can be filed to the Office for the Harmonization of the Internal Market (OHIM), Allicante Spain or to German Patent and Trademark Office (DPMA, Munich), the Austrian Patent Office (Ã–PAT, Vienna) or the European Patent Office (EPA, Munich).

The Attorney provides patent applications for international patents according the patent cooperation treaty (pct), national german patents or european patents.

Trademark registration can be achived for German Trademark, Austrian Trademark, European Community Trademark or international registered Trademark according to Madrid Protocol (MMA or PMMA).
